formatted_address: 399 Yung Sheng Rd, #01-45/46 Taman Jurong Shopping Centre, Singapore 610399
name: 399 Kitchen

reviews.text: On Friday 27 December 2024, I had black pepper chicken with rice for my lunch at the 399 food court at Taman Jurong Shopping Centre, and I liked this meal as the black pepper chicken with rice tasted very delicious. Overall, the service provided to me was very good and I would love to try these other delightful dishes from this outlet (except pork and beef) in the future.
